{"tid":125763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警判刑】顧紀筠出席撐警遊行：法治彰顯，卻痛失公義！","createTime":"2017-02-18T18:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:58:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1631e41ccc92f842086d3d23df3b2f9d01db5e","tid":125763,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"七警罪成，各被判入獄2年，不准緩刑。香港政研會今日發起撐警有效執法大遊行，現場有約千人參與，包括多個親建制組織。港大校委會成員盧寵茂及藝人顧紀筠亦有到場撐警。<br />\n<br />\n香港政研會主席鄧德成指，近日是香港最傷感、法治最黑暗日子，七警被判史無前例2年，批評司法摧毀警隊士氣。有人扮演法官，遭多人作勢毆打。(新聞連結: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lvlmrX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lvlmrX&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=93daa4a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lvlmrX</a> )<br />\n顧紀筠晚上以短訊回覆《蘋果》表示：「我們在香港成長，香港係一個法治的社會，令我們感到安全。但今次七警案的判決，令我感到痛心，失望！法治彰顯，卻痛失公義！所以要表達我的感受。」  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170218/large/1487429111_a0ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170218%2Flarge%2F1487429111_a0ee.jpg&h=7578ae43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170218/56323137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170218%2F56323137&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=35ce7fad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170218%2F56323137&h=5d280692\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170218/56323137</a>"},{"pid":"c6eda97a8a8cfa9a5aaeee427d6d4a01256dab1d","tid":125763,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"哇呢句有文有路喎"},{"pid":"02aba508eb01060fcddc4b7d6d64cfb8e21bc6f8","tid":125763,"uid":19807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"好快就會見唔到佢個仔上cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa3f3bfaadbb5c039787c20a39d861138bd8ef2","tid":125763,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"判<span style=\"color: red;\">史無前例</span>2年?<br />\n<br />\n法官杜大衛在判刑時引用上訴庭案例，強調必須對犯法警員判阻嚇性刑罰。過往也曾發生過紀律部隊人員在執勤期間打人的案件，他們面對不同控罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">刑期由10個月至兩年半不等</span>。其中比較轟動的是反黑組高級督察李志輝，他將的士高經理拉入後巷毆打，再砌生豬肉屈經理阻差辦公，被判監兩年半。<br />\n李志輝案發生於2001年，他被控妨礙司法公正及普通襲擊兩罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">經審訊後在區院被裁定兩罪成立，分別被判兩年及半年監禁，分期執行。</span>法官在判刑時斥責被告行為令警隊蒙羞，動搖市民對司法制度和警隊的信心，決定判處阻嚇性刑罰。案件中，證人被毆打約7分鐘，頭部紅腫要留院一天。"},{"pid":"5ae9cef063965497ed0d2787f6b58e16075e1d29","tid":125763,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"佢想點呀？法治彰顯，咪公義囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3742b70ab38d736b5b371c2135c422bc790bef14","tid":125763,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"用私刑唔使坐就係公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124cad260f1163d0d307c2489d633c357d118ad0","tid":125763,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:30:46.000Z","msg":"點撚樣失去公義法呀？<br />\n八婆你解釋比我聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02cae6ab74ab1b37019326e826d5e8458d6fc3d","tid":125763,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:32:08.000Z","msg":"之前有ching 成日J佢"},{"pid":"30d1457a5f5ce31b25c81888c3a87f71795ded38","tid":125763,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"黃藍做乜咁鬼易分<br />\n普遍無創意，認真唔識笑果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca7b7b14243916174472f45446451d6ff5de257","tid":125763,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:45:43.000Z","msg":"條女好撚正<img src